Check Recipients
----------------

This add-on for Mozilla Thunderbird checks for the existence of email addresses of all recipients in Compose message window through local address books and LDAP directories.

This add-on is written in XUL and Javascript.

Trustedbird/Milimail project
URL: http://www.trustedbird.org
